-- The Real Deal: Which U.S. Banks Would Survive?
-- B y
-- 2012-03-13T10:41:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-13/the-real-deal-which-u-s-banks-would-survive-.html
Bloomberg's Mike McKee reports 
that the  Federal Reserve , exercising sweeping new authority to 
ensure financial stability, will show how the capital of the 19 
largest U.S. banks might fare through a deep recession and a 
second housing crisis and use the results to dictate which of 
them can increase their dividends. He speaks on Bloomberg 
Television's "Inside Track." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 03:19
 